### Check B is alive
GET http://localhost:8082/actuator/health

### Read stock
GET http://localhost:8082/inventory/SKU-1001

### Place an order (A calls B internally)
POST http://localhost:8081/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{"sku": "SKU-1001", "quantity": 3}

### Try insufficient stock — should be 409, not 503
POST http://localhost:8081/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{"sku": "SKU-1003", "quantity": 1}

### Service A health
GET http://localhost:8081/actuator/health